                <p><strong>Video Scholarship Contest Rules and Regulations</strong></p>
                <ul><li>Entrants must be 18 years or older.</li>
                <li>Participants must have internet access, provide a valid e-mail address and have a video recording device.</li>
                <li>Winners will be notified by e-mail only.</li>
                <li>No purchase necessary.</li>
